<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.9">
<l>piṇaṅkaḷiṭu kāṭataṉuḷ naṭamāṭu piññakaṉō</l>
<l>ṭiṇaṅkutiruc cakkarattem perumāṉārk kiṭamvicumpil</l>
<l>kaṇaṅkaḷiyaṅ kummallaik kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉam</l>
<l>vaṇaṅkumaṉat tāravarai vaṇaṅkeṉṟaṉ maṭaneñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My own simple heart, worship those whose minds worship in Talacayaṉam</l>
<l>At Mallai by the great sea where crowds from heaven travel,</l>
<l>The place for our lord with the sacred discus, who is conjoined with him</l>
<l>Of matted locks who dances in the ghat where corpses are placed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
